OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1784751301
OL,3,CTwo of PC Andrew Harper's killers may
OL,4,Cbe eligible for early release
OL,6,FThe mother of Thames Valley police
OL,7,Fofficer Andrew Harper has said it
OL,8,Ffeels like an "insult" that two of her
OL,9,Fson's killers may be eligible for
OL,10,Fearly release from prison.
OL,12,FPC Harper was 28 years old when he
OL,13,Fsustained fatal injuries while
OL,14,Fresponding to a quad bike theft in
OL,15,FSulhamstead, Berkshire, in August 2019.
OL,17,FHe died after getting caught in a
OL,18,Fstrap attached to the back of a car
OL,19,Fand dragged down a country road as
OL,20,Fthree teenage suspects fled the scene
OL,21,Fof the burglary.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,389,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1784751301
OL,3,CTwo of PC Andrew Harper's killers may
OL,4,Cbe eligible for early release
OL,6,FJessie Cole and Albert Bowers, who
OL,7,Fwere passengers in the car and both 17
OL,8,Fyears old at the time, were handed 13
OL,9,Fyears in custody for manslaughter
OL,10,Fafter a trial at the Old Bailey in
OL,11,F2020.
OL,13,FBoth men might be eligible to be
OL,14,Freleased from prison halfway through
OL,15,Ftheir sentences, the Ministry of
OL,16,FJustice (MoJ) has confirmed.
OL,18,FUnder the new Sentencing Act, set to
OL,19,Fcome into force in September, some
OL,20,F6,000 criminals are set to be released
OL,21,Funder the early prison release scheme.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,389,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1784751301
OL,3,CTwo of PC Andrew Harper's killers may
OL,4,Cbe eligible for early release
OL,6,FThe Government has so far failed to
OL,7,Frule out whether killers, rapists and
OL,8,Fpaedophiles will be exempt from the
OL,9,Fscheme.
OL,11,FThe driver of the vehicle which caused
OL,12,FPC Harper's death, Henry Long,
OL,13,Freceived a 16-year sentence, and will
OL,14,Fnot be eligible for the scheme.
OL,16,FPC Harper's mother Debbie Adlam said
OL,17,Fshe had received a letter from the MoJ
OL,18,Fconfirming their sentences might be
OL,19,Freduced.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,389,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1784751301
OL,3,CTwo of PC Andrew Harper's killers may
OL,4,Cbe eligible for early release
OL,6,FShe said: "It makes me feel sick.
OL,7,FAndrew's life doesn't get to come
OL,8,Fback. It feels like a slap in the face
OL,9,Fand an insult."
OL,11,FShe added that "people are getting a
OL,12,Ffree pass for crime" in the UK.
OL,14,FA Ministry of Justice spokesperson
OL,15,Fsaid: "This was a horrific crime, and
OL,16,Four deepest sympathies are with PC
OL,17,FAndrew Harper's family and friends.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,389,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1784751301
OL,3,CTwo of PC Andrew Harper's killers may
OL,4,Cbe eligible for early release
OL,6,F"In 2024, the country was facing a
OL,7,Fprison crisis and a total breakdown of
OL,8,Flaw and order, with judges ordered to
OL,9,Fstop jailing dangerous criminals.
OL,11,F"This government is committed to
OL,12,Fpublic safety: we are building prison
OL,13,Fplaces at the fastest rate since the
OL,14,FVictorian era, and taking the
OL,15,Fdifficult decisions needed to lock up
OL,16,Fthe most dangerous offenders."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,389,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1784751301
OL,3,CTwo of PC Andrew Harper's killers may
OL,4,Cbe eligible for early release
OL,6,FThe Government has insisted that the
OL,7,Fact will not see early releases for
OL,8,Foffenders deemed "the most dangerous",
OL,9,Fincluding those on extended
OL,10,Fdeterminate or life sentences.
OL,12,FThe Police Federation for England and
OL,13,FWales responded on X, calling the
OL,14,Fearly release policy "disgusting".
OL,16,FIts deputy national chair, Brian
OL,17,FBooth, said: "Police officers from
OL,18,Facross the country stood side by side
OL,19,Fto honour Andrew Harper at his funeral.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,389,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1784751301
OL,3,CTwo of PC Andrew Harper's killers may
OL,4,Cbe eligible for early release
OL,6,F"They and every serving officer will
OL,7,Fbe utterly sickened at the prospect of
OL,8,FBowers and Cole being back on the
OL,9,Fstreets so soon"
OL,11,FPC Harper responded to the quad bike
OL,12,Fcall just hours after he had been due
OL,13,Fto clock off and begin his honeymoon
OL,14,Fwith wife Lissie Harper.
OL,16,FAfter her husband's death, she
OL,17,Fcampaigned for legal changes to see
OL,18,Fharsher sentences for the manslaughter
OL,19,Fof emergency workers on duty.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,389,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38808
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1784751301
OL,3,CTwo of PC Andrew Harper's killers may
OL,4,Cbe eligible for early release
OL,6,FHarper's Law was among the new
OL,7,Fmeasures in the Police, Crime,
OL,8,FSentencing and Courts Act.
OL,10,FThe move extends mandatory life
OL,11,Fsentences to anyone who commits the
OL,12,Fmanslaughter of an emergency worker on
OL,13,Fduty, including police, prison
OL,14,Fofficers, firefighters and paramedics.
OL,16,FIt is not retrospective, meaning PC
OL,17,FHarper's killers cannot have their
OL,18,Fsentences extended.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,389,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38809
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1784751301
OL,3,CTwo of PC Andrew Harper's killers may
OL,4,Cbe eligible for early release
OL,6,FNew Justice Secretary Alex Norris has
OL,7,Fbeen urged to reconsider the early
OL,8,Frelease scheme after being appointed
OL,9,Fby Andy Burnham on Monday.
OL,11,FAsked about reports that the Prime
OL,12,FMinister could be working on exempting
OL,13,Frapists and child groomers from the
OL,14,Fscheme, his spokesman said: "The
OL,15,FGovernment's fully focused on keeping
OL,16,Fthe public safe.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G9/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,389,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38810
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1784751301
OL,3,CTwo of PC Andrew Harper's killers may
OL,4,Cbe eligible for early release
OL,6,F"We've got no option but to take
OL,7,Fdecisive action to fix the crisis in
OL,8,Four prisons. I'm not going to get into
OL,9,Fspeculation over possible policy
OL,10,Fchanges.
OL,12,F"Of course, the Prime Minister will
OL,13,Ftake decisions on all manner of policy
OL,14,Fareas in the future, including how we
OL,15,Fget justice for victims."
OL,17,FAileen O'Connor, Chair of Thames
OL,18,FValley Police Federation, said: "The
OL,19,Fkillers of PC Andrew Harper should be
OL,20,Fkept where they belong... behind bars."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G10/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,389,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38811
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1784751301
OL,3,CTwo of PC Andrew Harper's killers may
OL,4,Cbe eligible for early release
OL,6,FShe continued: "These killers have
OL,7,Fnever shown any remorse for their
OL,8,Fhorrific and deadly actions that night.
OL,10,F"Andrew's wife Lissie and his whole
OL,11,Ffamily are serving a life sentence.
OL,12,FThe least we can expect is that his
OL,13,Fkillers serve their whole sentence.
OL,14,FHowever poor it already is.
OL,16,F"We will be taking this matter up with
OL,17,Fthe Police Minister, the Home
OL,18,FSecretary and the new Prime Minister.
OL,19,FWe will not stop. Andrew deserves
OL,20,Fnothing less.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G11/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,389,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38812
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1784751301
OL,3,CTwo of PC Andrew Harper's killers may
OL,4,Cbe eligible for early release
OL,6,F"What message does this send about the
OL,7,Fworth of a life of a police officer?
OL,8,FThe Government and the parole board
OL,9,Fmust reconsider any plans to release
OL,10,FAndrew's killers early.
OL,12,F"And they must do it now.
OL,14,F"No ifs. No buts."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G12/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
